[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（――今より遥か遠い昔。数多の勢力がこの世界の\n　覇権を賭けて争い合った、戦乱の時代があった）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00940",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（その戦いの裏で暗躍した諜報員。\n　それが「忍び」と呼ばれた者たち）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00941",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（乱世を生き延びた忍びは、その技術を後継者に伝え、\n　代々守り続けてきた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00942",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（拙者もまた、そうした忍びの一族の末裔。\n　本来ならば、家を継ぐのが役目ではある……が！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00943",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（寝ても覚めても修行ばかり！\n　遊びにも行けず、友達もできない！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00944",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "こんなの、もうたくさんじゃーーー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00945",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（――以来、家には一度も帰っていない）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00946",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（その気になれば拙者の居場所など筒抜けのはず。\n　しかし、これまで便りの１つもなかった）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00947",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それが今になって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00948",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "その様子では、あまり良い知らせではなさそうですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00949",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "社長殿……はは、貴殿に隠しごとはできませんな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00950",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……父が病を患ってしまったようです。すぐ命に関わる\nほどではないそうですが、いつ治るかも分からないと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00951",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そうでしたの……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00952",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "年明けにはこちらに迎えを寄こすそうです。\nそして、今後のことについて話したいと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00953",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "っ！　それは……つまり、\nあなたが家を継ぐかどうかという話を？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00954",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "十中八九そうでしょう。母が早くに他界したことも\nあり、拙者に兄弟はおりませぬ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00955",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者が継がねば、我らの系譜は途絶えてしまいますゆえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00956",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "それでは、アイドルの仕事は……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00957",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "もちろん、諦めなくてはなりません。\n古き伝統を重んじる父が、許してくださるはずもない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00958",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "それに、父がまだ動けるうちに、\n跡継ぎとしてやるべきことをやらねば",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00959",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "……すでに、覚悟は決めていますのね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00960",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……ええ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00961",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "いずれは、こういう時が来るだろうとは\n思っておりました。それが少々早まっただけのこと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00962",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "父には育ててもらった恩があります。\n母亡き後、世話を焼いてくれた家の者たちにも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00963",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ファンのみんなや、メンバーの二人、\nそして社長殿には申し訳ありませんが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00964",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "これ以上、身勝手なことはできませぬ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00965",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]